data.description: Brand New carpet in the basement as of 12/22/2023!  Come check out this great home in a great location and corner lot!! This home has a great living room addition you rarely see in this price range with lots of light. Updated kitchen, central air, very large Trex deck and huge fire pit area! Basement has a 4th bedroom, just doesn't have a closet, and a large storage room also with shelves. Fully fenced, and has a large gravel RV pad and a shed for storage. Nice big covered parking as well. Schedule a showing today!
